      "content": "hey, i've been getting these really bad migraines lately but this one is just different. it hit me super fast, like the worst headache i've ever had, and now my left cheek feels kinda weird and kind of heavy/droopy. i think i might just be having a really bad migraine episode, do u think it's just the migraine or should i be worried?",
