    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm kinda scared of going to the er though, it's so expensive and the wait is always hours. if it really is just a migraine, can i just take some extra ibuprofen and maybe some magnesium to sleep it off? i have some leftover prescription meds too, would it be okay to mix them with the ibuprofen if the pain doesn't go away?",
